# UI Project Context

This project uses modern HTML, Tailwind CSS, and component-based frontend design.

Default priorities:
1. Semantic HTML
2. Accessibility
3. Responsive design
4. Reusable components
5. Visual consistency
6. Performance
7. Maintainability

Do not generate random visual styles.

Before creating UI:
- Check existing components.
- Reuse existing spacing, colors, typography, and layout patterns.
- Prefer small reusable components.
- Avoid inline styles unless absolutely necessary.
- Avoid hardcoded magic values when Tailwind utilities or design tokens exist.

Use clean, modern, minimal UI by default.
